data.description: Want land and a show place?  Need a space for your Horse? This 3 Bedroom 2 bath home sits on 1.83 Acres.  This home has so many updates, hard to get them all in this small space.    Must see to appreciate the outstanding job these owners have made to the property.  Starting with new metal roof, Re-finish original hardwood flooring, kitchen updates with bar, new granite countertops, cabinets appliances, a mud room, 4th bedroom/study/office/game room, painting, new windows, ceilings Single Car Garage/ with work space = to a second car and more.  There is a small efficiency unit with an entrance from Garage and/or outside. The back of the property has a creek with small pond; a large portion of the property is fenced.  See for yourself!
